OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1780661502
OL,3,CMan killed and six people injured
OL,4,Cafter Honda crashed into Chinese
OL,5,Ctakeaway
OL,7,FA 48-year-old man has died and
OL,8,Fmultiple people, including four
OL,9,Fchildren, are injured after a car
OL,10,Fcrash into a takeaway.
OL,12,FMedics were called to the scene at
OL,13,Fjust before 10:30pm and found the
OL,14,Fdriver, a 48-year-old man, with
OL,15,Fserious injuries. He died a short time
OL,16,Flater. A woman in the passenger seat
OL,17,Fwas seriously injured and rushed to
OL,18,Fhospital.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
