FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1780661502
OL,3,CMan killed and six people injured
OL,4,Cafter Honda crashed into Chinese
OL,5,Ctakeaway
OL,7,FTwo boys and two girls who were also
OL,8,Fin the car were taken to the hospital,
OL,9,Fnone of their injuries is believed to
OL,10,Fbe life-threatening.
OL,12,FPolice have since launched an
OL,13,Finvestigation following the car crash.
OL,15,FThe Honda Civic hit a Canotese and
OL,16,FEnglish takeaway restaurant on High
OL,17,FStreet in Princes End, Tipton, on
OL,18,FTuesday.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1780661502
OL,3,CMan killed and six people injured
OL,4,Cafter Honda crashed into Chinese
OL,5,Ctakeaway
OL,7,FA cyclist who was passing at the time
OL,8,Fwas treated for minor injuries at the
OL,9,Fscene.
OL,11,FWest Midlands Police confirmed an
OL,12,Finvestigation has been launched and
OL,13,Fsaid, "We are investigating after a
OL,14,Fman has sadly died following a
OL,15,Fcollision in Tipton last night.
OL,17,F"Just before 10.20pm, we were called
OL,18,Fto High Street in Princes End after a
OL,19,Fvehicle hit a property.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1780661502
OL,3,CMan killed and six people injured
OL,4,Cafter Honda crashed into Chinese
OL,5,Ctakeaway
OL,7,F"Despite the best efforts of
OL,8,Fparamedics, the driver of the Honda
OL,9,FCivic, a 48-year-old man, died at the
OL,10,Fscene.
OL,12,F"Our thoughts are with his loved ones
OL,13,Fat this tragic time.
OL,15,F"There were five other occupants in
OL,16,Fthe vehicle, including a woman and
OL,17,Ffour children, who have all been taken
OL,18,Fto hospital for treatment.
OL,20,F"Thankfully, their injuries are not
OL,21,Fbelieved to be life-threatening.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1780661502
OL,3,CMan killed and six people injured
OL,4,Cafter Honda crashed into Chinese
OL,5,Ctakeaway
OL,7,F"The road was closed overnight and has
OL,8,Fnow reopened. Our Serious Collision
OL,9,FInvestigation Unit (SCIU) is keen to
OL,10,Fhear from anyone who has CCTV or
OL,11,Fdashcam footage from around the area,
OL,12,Fand anyone who saw the collision
OL,13,Fshould get in touch with us."
OL,15,FA spokesperson for West Midlands
OL,16,FAmbulance Service added: "Crews
OL,17,Farrived to find a car which had been
OL,18,Finvolved in a collision with a
OL,19,Fbuilding.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1780661502
OL,3,CMan killed and six people injured
OL,4,Cafter Honda crashed into Chinese
OL,5,Ctakeaway
OL,7,F"The driver, a man, was in a critical
OL,8,Fcondition. He received advanced life
OL,9,Fsupport on scene but was sadly
OL,10,Fconfirmed deceased by ambulance staff
OL,11,Fa short time later.
OL,13,F"A woman passenger sustained serious
OL,14,Finjuries, and ambulance crews
OL,15,Fadministered trauma care before she
OL,16,Fwas conveyed to Midland Metropolitan
OL,17,FUniversity Hospital. Two boys from the
OL,18,Fcar sustained minor injuries and were
OL,19,Fconveyed in the same ambulance to
OL,20,Fhospital.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1780661502
OL,3,CMan killed and six people injured
OL,4,Cafter Honda crashed into Chinese
OL,5,Ctakeaway
OL,7,F"Two girls from the car suffered
OL,8,Fpotentially serious injuries and
OL,9,Freceived trauma care from the team of
OL,10,Fmedics before both were taken on blue
OL,11,Flights and sirens to Birmingham
OL,12,FChildren's Hospital for further care.
OL,14,F"A man, believed to be a passing
OL,15,Fcyclist, sustained minor injuries and
OL,16,Fwas discharged on scene and left in
OL,17,Fthe care of relatives."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
